Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:20.51,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(298,0)}We sigh whenever we're about to come to a standstill
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:26.77,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}While moving on this endless journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:34.49,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Everytime we lunge for it, it escapes and flies off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:41.91,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}But now, there's nothing to be afraid of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:49.83,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}The powerful ties that bind our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:55.30,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Will never come loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:05.02,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9}After a lifetime of searching, we finally arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:10.81,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Here, where the period lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:20.11,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}Let's change all our sorrow and rage to power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:25.04,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,298}Destiny is right within our reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:20.51,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(298,0)}終わりなき旅の途中　立ち止まりそうな時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:26.77,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}深いため息こぼす　僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:34.49,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}掴みかけてはまた離れていった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:41.91,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}でも今はもう何も恐れることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:49.83,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}心を繋ぐ強い絆は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:55.30,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}けして解けはしないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:05.02,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9}探し続けて辿り着いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:10.81,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}この場所で {\fsp8}Perio{\fsp3.2}d に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:20.11,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}悲しみ怒り 力に変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:25.04,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,298}運命はすぐそばに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:20.51,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(298,0)}Owarinaki tabi no tochuu tachidomarisouna toki
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:26.77,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Fukai tameiki kobosu bokura wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:34.49,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Tsukamikaketewa mata hanareteitta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:41.91,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Demo ima wa mou nanimo osoreru koto wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:49.83,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}Kokoro wo tsunagu tsuyoi kizuna wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:55.30,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Keshite hodoke wa shinai sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:05.02,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9}Sagashitsuzukete tadoritsuita
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:10.81,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Kono basho de piriodo ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:20.11,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}Kanashimi ikari chikara ni kaete
