Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:49.49,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}The promise we never made
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:50.28,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:55.12,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}tries to snatch our future away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:22:00.71,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that we can't rejoice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:01.71,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}straight from the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:06.67,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}when we obtain something we've always been after?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:12.39,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,498}The overflowing tears aren't from feebleness or remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:17.18,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,258)}They're fragments born from agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:22.23,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Of all the moments and destinies,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:30.99,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I realized there's one absolute certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:33.53,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if things get tough and I'm at my limit
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:37.54,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:42.42,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:50.26,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can feel the warmth of your right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:53.93,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}where it's tightly joined with my left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:49.49,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}交わしたはずのない約束が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:50.28,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}今日も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:55.12,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}僕らの未来を奪おうとする
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:22:00.71,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,欲しがっていたものを手にしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:01.71,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}素直に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:06.67,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}うまく笑えないのはなぜだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:12.39,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,498}あふれる涙は　弱さや後悔じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:17.18,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,258)}イタミが生んだカケラで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:22.23,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}どんな瞬間だって運命だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:30.99,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}ひとつだけ確かなものがあると知った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:33.53,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,限界だって困難だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:37.54,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,あきらめたくないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:42.42,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,このまま離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:50.26,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}かたく握りしめた　君の右手のぬくもり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:53.93,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}ここにあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:49.49,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Kawashita hazu no nai yakasoku ga
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:50.28,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Kyou mo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:55.12,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}Bokura no mirai wo ubaou to suru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:22:00.71,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshigatteita mono wo te ni shitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:01.71,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Sunao ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:06.67,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}Umaku waraenai nowa nazedarou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:12.39,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,498}Afureru namida wo yowasa ya koukai ja nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:17.18,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,258)}Itami ga unda kakera de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:22.23,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Donna shunkan datte unmei datte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:30.99,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Hitotsu dake tashika na mono ga aru to shitta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:33.53,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Genkai datte konnan datte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:37.54,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Akirametakunaiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:42.42,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomama hanasanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:50.26,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Kataku nigirishimeta kimi no migite no nukumori
