Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.23,0:00:16.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Sir Kimblee?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.16,0:00:21.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is far from what you promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:26.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You said your soldiers in Briggs would betray the others if we were to carry the attack to the fort!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.80,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:39.04,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,That was a crushing victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:39.93,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:43.31,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,So this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:50.00,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,...is the bloody crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.09,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:39.17,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,...you're supposed to read the veins of the dragon while performing Eastern Alchemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:40.80,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't understand how!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:45.01,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to sharpen your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.18,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:47.47,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,See? I sense it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.06,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.44,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.27,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me the theories behind it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:53.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Things are real rowdy in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.15,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:56.53,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for having to ask you to hide us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:57.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:02:59.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're benefiting as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.53,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Not the hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Now the kids have someone new to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:15.92,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Let Zampano know that we're going up to the mountains to collect firewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.05,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:18.92,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:22.22,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,What a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:26.97,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell is Zampano?! Everyone else is working!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.02,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.44,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.69,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:43.45,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Zampano.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:53.96,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,So, you found out about Selim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:55.75,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.75,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,And my identity, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:00.05,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:08.47,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel as a citizen of a country...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:11.68,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,...to know that your leader and his son are both Homunculi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:18.82,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's a very sad thing for a family member you're supposed to trust to be fabricated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.20,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like you're playing house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:26.32,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,All the while pretending to be human, creatures you deem as fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:31.33,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,As you say, he's my "son" given to me by my handlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:35.37,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,My rank of Führer President, along with my men and everything else, was also given to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.09,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than "house", I'd say it's more accurate to say we're playing "politics".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:43.09,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,However, I picked my bride myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.72,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Is the tea still not ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.64,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.77,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:10.08,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so you used to be one of the head honchos of that Research Laboratory 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:14.33,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say that. I just had a couple of people working under me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.46,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how they're doing now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:21.67,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.34,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Who might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.76,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,He's a vagrant I met this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.56,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to have you see him, Doctor-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.47,Default-alt,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Zampano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:37.39,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,The shitty acting ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.86,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Why hello, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:45.94,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What might you be doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:52.62,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're being too optimistic if you think roaches like you can outwit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:56.62,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.62,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Zampano!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:04.42,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,The shitty acting ends here, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:09.22,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal from the start was to lure you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:12.05,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing how much of a nasty guy you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:16.52,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd come and hunt me yourself if you knew I was alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.81,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What can three pieces of trash like you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:22.48,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many you've got on your side,\Nyou're nothing but trash in the end-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.82,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,They work like landmines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:29.91,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy evolves every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.87,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way alchemy like that can exist-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.58,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.13,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,If they're mines...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:46.30,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,...all I have to do is trace your footsteps!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.13,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:54.97,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,They were made to only react to Homunculi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:07:00.39,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tell where they are and what awaits you because of all the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.94,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,So, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:06.98,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel to be ridiculed by people\Nyou've been looking down on as trash and scum?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.41,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,He's being fooled, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.78,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,It's just remote alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:17.95,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:23.33,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You scum should obey our commands, just as you were meant to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:27.67,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing but trash! Don't get too cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:45.77,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.36,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:54.74,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:58.45,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Grr. You're pretty fast for a fatass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.25,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.75,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You little shit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.92,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Such weak attacks can hardly pierce my skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.43,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:18.26,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about {\i1}this{\i0\fscx40} {\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.90,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Did he do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.74,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Got you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:39.87,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.54,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:43.46,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, I'll snap him in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:44.96,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.38,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,...you're in for some punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.71,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I warn you, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.76,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,By saying I'll destroy an entire village if you were to do something unnecessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:56.34,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.97,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going to resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.39,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.74,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll destroy those slums over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.32,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:20.20,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,But simply destroying them is no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:25.71,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I'll bring a few back to Central and make a philosopher's stone out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.21,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,You filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:30.13,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,You're still making those things over at Central?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.50,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Release the researchers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:33.71,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Release my men!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:34.21,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.80,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:40.30,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Because you see, we've already turned all of them into philosopher's stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:44.02,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,E-Even my men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:49.15,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Guess I forgot to tell you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:53.94,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,But Doctor, you shouldn't have any reason to weep {\i1}now{\i0\fscx40} {\r}, after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:58.82,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Since you've made so many philosopher's stones in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.74,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Using human lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:10.50,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:15.59,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I've made many philosopher's stones, sacrificing the lives of many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:20.39,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I am more familiar with the ways of making a\Nphilosopher's stone than anyone else in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:23.72,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing how to make one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:27.35,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,...also means I know how to destroy them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.59,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming from the hill where the doctor and the others are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.19,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.19,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! Oww! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:18.32,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.36,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:21.40,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:29.95,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:30.58,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,This-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.33,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.83,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Envy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:39.30,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could be defeated by you inferior beings...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.30,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.76,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Even the chimeras...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:45.35,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.10,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't look at-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:50.35,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down on me, humans!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:56.52,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me, you insects...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:57.90,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Little shits...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.28,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't... look...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:04.57,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,We were being manipulated by something like {\i1}this{\i0\fscx40} {\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.62,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,We won, Marcoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.26,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:27.30,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor Marcoh! What's with that wound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:31.18,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,What's {\i1}that{\i0\fscx40} {\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:40.11,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so you guys were doing some amazing things without us knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:44.32,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,This is what happens when you disobey us humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:49.83,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do something so reckless, Doctor Marcoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:53.58,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,All my life, I've been doing everything as ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:57.79,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,But this was the one thing I wanted to settle myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:01.13,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking on my own... Making a decision on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.59,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Just like your parents did things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:10.10,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,But please, try not to be so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:11.97,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.10,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.56,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.77,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Yoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.19,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:25.70,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I've taken over this guy's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.74,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:30.41,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.49,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,M-My body isn't listening to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.62,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,No use putting up a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.37,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.25,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to help this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.08,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, you can do whatever you want with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.96,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,He's not really our friend, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:45.30,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a short while, Sir Yoki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.26,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.05,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Master Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.26,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're{\i0\fscx40} {\r} on my side though, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:53.85,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.85,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look away, dammit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:02.52,Default-alt,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,I believed in you, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.48,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? I thought this guy was your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.94,Default-alt,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,I believed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:05.78,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Quit putting up a useless fight, Envy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.28,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, we don't exactly care about our actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:12.78,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to get in our way,\Nwe'll destroy you along with that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.66,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.04,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He came off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:17.96,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.62,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Nice act.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:24.38,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not very good at bluffs...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.76,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.84,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,None of you are my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:29.80,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Our friendship is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.14,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to do with you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:35.39,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:39.52,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's about time you tell us what you guys are up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.98,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.57,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.23,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Spill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.90,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Spill the beans, you insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:46.65,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.61,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Show him who's boss, Zampano!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:54.58,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell you, I'll just be killed later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.62,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I tell you, idiots?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:57.87,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:02.08,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, where's the Fullmetal runt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.33,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:05.46,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He should be in Briggs right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:06.71,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:10.09,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Last I heard, he was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.01,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.01,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.01,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:17.68,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a mine collapsed in Baschool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.39,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:21.56,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.44,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.61,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,So, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.20,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Should we head back to Baschool?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:36.45,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:38.49,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,In a situation like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:42.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,...Brother would definitely believe in the safety of the other team and keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:45.75,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.26,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hope is not lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.84,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to split off for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.76,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about it for a little while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:00.93,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of simply detesting this country for denying Ishbal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:02.69,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm going to work to change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:08.40,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,And for that, I need your help as well, Marcoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:11.99,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.03,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:16.78,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,To change this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:20.41,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, there's a city I want to visit, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.04,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.87,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Lior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:27.67,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,If my predictions are correct, that tunnel should be there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:32.17,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,May, take this thing and return to your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.05,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:37.47,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,It's the wreck of an immortal homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.22,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,With this, your clan may be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:44.23,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx89}B-But if I go back, who'll be here to help you with Eastern Alchemy-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.81,Default-alt,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx96}Is this really the time to be worrying about another country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.19,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to this country with a resolve that weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:32.17,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So I'm thinking it'll be fastest for us to just destroy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.43,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then, we'll be able to buy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:37.72,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}With the extra time, we can solve the structure of the new transmutation circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:43.48,Default-alt,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So, this "new transmutation circle" is the thing we discovered the other day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.06,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yup, that's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.73,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,If your clan happens to lose its struggle for power,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:54.49,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,what are you going to tell the people who placed their fate in your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:58.49,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,"I failed because I was too busy helping people from another country"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:01.95,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:05.96,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,We, the citizens of this country, will take care of it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:22.22,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.73,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, May.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:34.57,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Once we settle things here, I'll visit you to learn more about Eastern Alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:36.28,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Al...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.07,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.53,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:50.29,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.30,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.88,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.05,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:01.76,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.27,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we should get going, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:04.89,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Greed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.21,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,No luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:36.55,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Izumi Curtis is out on vacation with her husband, and no one knows when they'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.76,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Guess there's not much we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:43.22,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,We should head back and report this to Führer President Bradley for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Bradley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:53.48,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with me, Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:57.11,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Call someone to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.07,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:02.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to see Mr. Greed if I follow them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:03.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:25.43,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:29.02,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind moving your foot, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.10,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,You are to address me as "Major General" here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:34.11,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:37.86,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a cowardly face on as always, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:41.82,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the battle with Drachma ended with your crushing victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.57,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:47.95,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't that just speed up the completion of the Nationwide Transmutation Circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:49.00,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:53.62,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,What we must protect right now is the safety of the country itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:57.38,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,If there stands an enemy who threatens that very peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:20:01.09,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,...our job is to deliver an overwhelming defeat of perfection!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:04.26,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear... why must you act so fierce?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:07.01,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you'll never find someone to marry-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.10,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,You just lack the fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.02,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,You laggard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.81,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Being with you makes me feel cowardly as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Major General.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He's your brother, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.70,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want to think of him as my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:27.33,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,He's a coward who ran away from Ishbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:29.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:31.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:39.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aware of the three laws state alchemists are forbidden to disobey?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:40.92,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.55,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,"Do not oppose the military."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.88,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,"Do not make gold."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:46.43,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,And "Do not create humans."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:50.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The first law is self-explanatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:54.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The second law is put in place to avoid economic turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:57.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the third?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:01.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why does the nation forbid alchemists from creating humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:03.61,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I assume it's because of the moral and ethical implications.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:10.45,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Even among alchemists, I hear the act is tacitly forbidden as a blasphemy to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:13.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:19.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What is and is not ethical changes with time and also depends on whom you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:24.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That is not the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:31.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It is to prevent an individual from creating a powerful army of their own, Major General.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:04.57,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,This place is in ruins...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:07.28,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really a place to eat around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:10.53,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... I know it was around here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:13.82,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:14.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:16.45,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,I should be asking you the same thing, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:18.58,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're still on a journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.25,0:23:20.79,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:23.08,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:25.09,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,Al, where's Ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:26.34,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,He's not with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:29.38,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,B-Brother isn't with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:32.72,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.39,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:38.60,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:40.18,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.18,0:23:43.69,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just pondering the meaning behind that mysterious look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:45.40,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Quit saying weird things!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:47.23,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:49.15,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I finished washing the pots!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.15,0:23:50.44,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else for me to-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:24:01.08,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Reunion. Revival. Resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:03.79,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come to set the soul afire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:07.67,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they live, humans continue to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:11.17,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how thorny the path may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:16.39,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:20.72,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 44, Revving at Full Throttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.68,0:24:23.02,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.02,0:24:25.86,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the beginning.
